Hi Christophe,

If you are using both sides of the dual-vac distributor, then yes.

Another option is to set up that engine with the retard side capped off 
and the engine timed to idle at 7.5 BTDC.

IIRC, the 0 notch should align to the nut on the hub.
http://type2.com/library/electrip/timemark.htm
http://www.ratwell.com/technical/FindTimingMark.html


